    {
      "id": "3b1bba46_8e4393fb",
      "file_path": "cps-application/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 176,
      "message": "NB: Can we enable conditional execution?\n\nIf we want the plugin to only run under certain conditions (e.g., only in certain profiles or phases), we can use profile-specific executions or property-based activation.\n\nFor example, we can add a profile to enable the plugin only for release builds \n:\n\n<profiles>\n    <profile>\n        <id>release-build</id>\n        <build>\n            <plugins>\n                <plugin>\n                    <groupId>io.github.git-commit-id</groupId>\n                    ...\n                    ....\n    </build>\n    </profile>\n</profiles>\n\n\nThis approach improves maintainability by reducing the scope of the plugin execution.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7957,
        "name": "Sourabh Sourabh",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "sourabh.sharma.lnf@gmail.com",
        "username": "sourabh_sourabh"
      },
      "updated": "2024-10-16 12:58:43.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
