      "id": "c1eeefd7_bcae360b",
      "file_path": "cps-application/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 197,
      "message": "Add this to your properties section at the top of your pom.xml:\n\n\n<properties>\n<git.properties.file>${project.build.outputDirectory}/git.properties</git.properties.file>\n</properties>\n\n<generateGitPropertiesFilename>${git.properties.file}</generateGitPropertiesFilename>\n\nNow, the filename can be changed globally through the properties section without editing the plugin configuration directly.",
      "author": {
